# Contribution Guidelines

When contributing to the ignite-cli project:

1. Follow the existing code structure:
   - Put new command implementations in [src/commands/](mdc:src/commands)
   - Put utility functions in [src/utils/](mdc:src/utils)
   - Add new templates in the appropriate [src/templates/](mdc:src/templates) subdirectory

2. Use the existing logging functions from [logger.sh](mdc:src/utils/logger.sh) for consistent output

3. Validate user inputs using functions from [validators.sh](mdc:src/utils/validators.sh)

4. Handle errors properly and report appropriate log messages

5. Test your changes thoroughly with different input combinations
